{"type": "article", "id": 40350, "title": "Gucci 发布新香水，以及，宜家购物袋款的帽子也出现了 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-05-02T02:48:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 7001, "name": "购物袋"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 40003, "name": "Boston Club"}, {"id": 40004, "name": "interparfums"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170502103225lJzGCkIPBfLmq63V.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/watches/could-breitling-deal-signal-more-consolidation-in-luxury-watches-10877388/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>行业不景气，瑞士独立钟表品牌 Breitling 被收购</strong></a> | 日前， Breitling 被 CVC 资本收购，这意味着市场上位于前 15 位的奢侈钟表品牌仅剩 Patek Philippe、Chopard 与 Audemars Piguet 未被收购。由于行业不景气，分析师认为该领域的收购并购活动还将继续，不过开云、LVMH 以及中国买家表现并不积极，说明他们仍然不看好这个市场。 </p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/interparfums-first-quarter-revenue-increases-34/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>世界上最大的香水集团 Interparfums 发财报，第一季度营收大涨了 34%</strong></a> | 法国香水集团 Interparfums 今年第一季度营收上涨了 34%，至 1.124 亿欧元。财报称，本次的业绩上涨得益于过去的六个月里，新发布的几款香水产品（包括 Coach, Jimmy Choo, Lanvin 和 Rochas 等品牌）的推动，该集团 CEO Philippe Benacin 预测，2017 年 Interparfums 集团的收入将达到 3.9 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/gucci-alessandro-michele-coty-debut-bloom-fragrance-10877157/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Gucci 发布了首款由创意总监 Alessandro Michele 设计的香水</strong></a> | 这款香水名为 Bloom，它由 Alessandro Michele 和调香大师 Alberto Morillas 合作完成，混合了天然茉莉、夜来香、鸢尾以及金银花。香水将是 Alessandro Michele 自 2015 年 1 月上任以来，为 GUCCI 带来一系列变革的延伸，同时也是更容易拉近和千禧一代距离的低门槛产品，而 Gucci 在全球的香水市场份额据估计有 6 亿美元。这款 Bloom 共有 30ml、50ml、100ml 三种容量，售价分别是 70、92、125 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101648np0U7flmY5WzbXhr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>来自日本井鯖江市的眼镜品牌 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/boston-club-releases-a-2017-spring-summer-paris-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boston Club 的 2017 春夏系列 lookbook </a>还挺好看的，来看看：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102318n7AHSGzlPLO4iuRh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102320mKeUDXqRcxN3BlVk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102320XQR9vf5x2JOLoI3Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102318UWnCDQ1uoXmxTl8M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102319Ry731iv8pYKPVnOU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102319WiSIoJqguG8B2fAk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102319Pr4ohJkuIZ7lfAyc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102333BTEXNiu8kLgbZFxH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102333IotMJkXnLdA2GN49.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705021023346mAJR0yZjtGnEesC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102319hzK6ZA2lmsk1BCIE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102333HS18QdYJMtDTwG7j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>日本潮牌 Undercover 找来了九谷烧 KUTANI SEAL 合作，推出了以<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/undercover-kutani-seal-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">单眼红苹果为主角的时尚瓷器系列</a>。整个联名将于 5 月 3 日至 14 日在新宿伊势丹 3 楼的 Undercover Pop-Up Shop 及大阪 LUCUA 1100 内的 Undercover 专门店发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102356HxDjwnmuBbzk8SWl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102356itYbAuDja6sXfe92.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102356EXtZfx1hLCNksqFD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102355XSxbOwcNUBZCesf3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102355Dq5E4YlkgoUW0mip.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102356Q3KYNT6OPgnuep1x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102356gtXud2eJqLa7Roj1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Nike 推出了以 Air Huarache 为原型的女版全新凉鞋<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/nike-air-huarache-huarache-ultra\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Air Huarache Huarache Ultra</a>，这款凉鞋运用了柔软皮革和透气编织材质，将于 5 月 3 日正式发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102214ZXNrdweGH127OiKc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102214CyETsmokRHUN0OfG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705021022142cr4wslXo9UYpSxL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102220brvByN219sZpjdAH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>优衣库今年的 UT 系列，以任天堂为主题，共收集了 16000 份设计作品。日前，优衣库从中挑选了 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/01/uniqlo-nintendo-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">25 件入选设计</a>，将于 5 月 19 日正式发布。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101902CMNWGlyLYKBm0S5O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101900JBAY8bdhTRqkvPxz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101900Z10KplPWRBzENH6h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101900xCGL0sEFW3bTVyje.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101901SagzXycksCj9dMfP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101901S8UQD9tqnilaybN1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101901LpZu9vn0bW2U1BzS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101902ykT3C7BuKrHzqseO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101902PhCXzOIbAB2gJS3R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101902H6DWjU5MCncGwNhT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101903REtHGnNMmKB2iWsy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101903eXnradK8CAJV0q5h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101903cBszgN6Sy0Kr7qEJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101903zQw14rmMVaSpFucq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101904LAPrEiwm5b0C8xBd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101904O7u2lLrfebJmS1ZU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101904FICb1aeyOuKckTGx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101905XE5KU3xtGubjO6ke.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101905mtZhsTvbLkDWCSBg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101942o56yXZvs4zTGxba2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705021019426TdJftcpIukDGrVy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101949PqjwDuFREdzAiG3J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101949WxZchvXg4RyBdPlq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102128yiJGZ8e9VTPFKIzv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102128fbnZPAQR5EJU1xHe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502102200cjCd6SDpwXi7ys9k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>受前段时间沸沸扬扬的巴黎世家版宜家购物袋事件启发，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/01/ikea-bag-hat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">洛杉矶街头品牌 Pleasure 与 China Town 联手，把宜家购物袋改造成了一款帽子</a>，还效仿宜家给出了一个真假辨别指南。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101822xhe8p5gl1QACBEq7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101822mT0XY5iJW4jDKfcq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101823RzmrkEonqvZC92wp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101823rUVBbyG0i4pu3ZYS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101822P9uJFb0lSOAzrkKG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170502101824CIjzfDtcNeWpmVQo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/01/ikea-bag-hat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a>、<a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/gucci-alessandro-michele-coty-debut-bloom-fragrance-10877157/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}